# Serverless reminder with Step Function, API Gateway, Lambda and S3
====================================================================


Access to a static web site hosted in S3, making a http post to an
API Gateway integrated with the lambda function
---------------------------------------------------------------------

The lambda function integrated role will launch a step machine
The steps function running the lambda functions will use SES and SNS
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Create a new REST PI Gateway to integrate with the state machine and
the lambda function
---------------------------------------------------------------------

